    ('en', 'african-forest-elephant', 'The quiet rainforest giant animal', 'The African Forest Elephant moves through thick rainforest like a living path-maker, opening space and spreading seeds as it goes. It is smaller than the savannah elephant, but in the forest it feels just as powerful. In human life, that means our best results often come from understanding what we are built for and using it well.'),
